thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Liande Automatic Equipment sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 124.51 pct to 151.04 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Liande Automatic Equipment sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit up 124.51 pct to 151.04 pct

organizations.name: shenzhen liande automatic equipment co ltd

text:
March 9(Reuters) - Shenzhen Liande Automatic Equipment Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2018 Q1 net profit to increase by 124.51 percent to 151.04 percent, or to be 11 million yuan to 12.3 million yuan
* Says FY 2017 Q1 net profit was 4.9 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is increased sales revenue of main business Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/5JyMLq Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
